{"tid":1380653,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂 穩軍心]作為前線 我有個好大既疑問","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T06:11:25.000Z","uid":137632,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"40aa25356d5228490121905bb49f67d5ae0cab66","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"小弟琴日開左個post問到底每一次看似冇目的咁守係為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379263/page/6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379263/page/6</a><br />\n相信有唔少人無論係前中後排都會咁問自己<br />\n為左方便各位，我整理左少少大家既意見 有遺漏既麻煩大家幫我補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先 quote返 #102535 完喇好嗎 既睇法      #142<br />\n<br />\n其實有時真係會無7月1嗰日咁有明確嘅目的<br />\n但每個星期出嚟十八區遊行確實係需要<br />\n個人認為目的或者效果有以下兩點<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 喚醒該區居民</span></strong><br />\n居民親身體驗警察如何對待示威者 勝過我地講千言萬語<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 為抗爭運動保溫</span></strong><br />\n香港人係善忘 每個禮拜提醒佢地係必需<br />\n亦都向政府同警察施加壓力<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>優點有三</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 勇武 和理非分工清晰 合作難度低 減低互屌分化機會</span></strong><br />\n勇武定位就係直面警察，比和理非可以安全撤離<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和理非負責嗌口號</span></strong>，傳遞訊息比嗰區嘅人知道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 前線可以保留體力，更長時間築起防線</strong></span><br />\n勇武唔洗參與全個遊行，節省體力<br />\n遊行前預先決定防線位置，到場直接開始建立防線<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 和理非遊行被警察驅趕，加強高牆與雞蛋嘅效果</span></strong><br />\n幾次警察嘅記者會都講話係示威者使用暴力在先，警察逼不得已先採取最低武力，已經非常克制<br />\n我地就利用和理非，完全0威脅，警察一武力驅趕就可以撕破佢嘅假面具<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">而以下就係我總結得出黎既內容</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一，死守係冇意思</span></span></strong><br />\n要撚狗我都要做既係打hit and run<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同升級<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第二，我地需要一個明確既目標</span></span></strong><br />\n可以係反衝上去 (需要真係人數夠多但夠齊心)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以簡單啲嘗試占據重要地方<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三，前排同中後排分工需要更清楚</span></span></strong><br />\n大家會咁諗，其中一個原因就係未搵到自己定位<br />\n所以 攻/盾/救火先好係前排<br />\n後排可以主力嗌口號，幫手update情況，最理想係前排一出聲就可以全世界一齊hit and run 打完就轉場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n費事打咁多冇人睇，有人想知我再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a3219d370299d528ecee6e866505659104e5adf4","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:25:16.000Z","msg":"推上去，我要解答大家依家想問但又唔敢問既問題"},{"pid":"cdee3d9a9b9fdcf223a6b7521e86bf66039b38df","tid":1380653,"uid":290385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"335fe3caaf92a0e64cc797798e2a12feef70cfdb","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:25:43.000Z","msg":"8月5號齊罷工就夠晒目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5daa95a4b736ce1ed36833de75de821b81bbd108","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:30:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6a74c8d93f286baea194cfdf374e79e44dda9f","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"挑戰十連"},{"pid":"b47b7f24160328cdcd7f8cea04817aeb81bb2d68","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"dd0cebedb24249321a1e64581e6532470f19de49","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"72da4be5f4f51c925c97e9a9b5508620c60ac76b","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:33:21.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"6f67fe9627bae2201c1a1f786f744a2b1cc92940","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"eb72a546f74f398927d5453e4b8872008392f5a0","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:34:28.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"3431bd159ae89d5575285a4c6c03b9d16860d71b","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:34:47.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"9c31503b3126333f0811ebb3814a83fc86a0301b","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"七<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69853c3d56cc93a1f4e477912233994a7aef5a4","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:35:10.000Z","msg":"八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0644ad3e156e99a259bca93fd2fd0256010f3540","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae8a3b0704e7581e7e25bd4c63d89e3f6c787f7","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"十<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e1d43552d90ca8d78c76f558fbf40a34a1b83c","tid":1380653,"uid":274055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"關於目標：<br />\n[前線心態調整] 我係勇武，我覺得衝，都要目標導向，Mission/Goal/Objective-Oriented<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378355</a>"},{"pid":"1af8d9d4843ae0443d3adfa4e1360627c1a71073","tid":1380653,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d0057d467609b5c41c56ba46147f17588bda01","tid":1380653,"uid":282747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"Pushh"},{"pid":"6602d0485f2423b4f509e37541d4107068752df0","tid":1380653,"uid":78857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:46:18.000Z","msg":"推 辛苦前線 不分化不割 光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"7ba3244c6cdbf3bb317d6efbf4c0c848d3af5fb4","tid":1380653,"uid":137632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"2ca5b426e235a94375003aa34ee7b83ce51fc912","tid":1380653,"uid":52621,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:48:59.000Z","msg":"總結好撚啱<br />\n721之後 死守真係冇意思 要攻就hit and run"},{"pid":"0695b3f075643539a19676fc12da4ee970eb6b35","tid":1380653,"uid":277011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":